{"type":"tool_execution_end","toolCallId":"call_29510752ff944bee866475","toolName":"mcp","result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C1\ncase_id: arb-ex10-20260630103350\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C1\nremaining_ms: 884671\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex10-20260630103350\",\"member_id\":\"C1\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"evidence\":[{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T11:54:17Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_2b6994532a43_submitted-evidence-07-defendant-2b6994532a43\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-07-defendant-2b6994532a43.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Supports defense argument that public discourse and secondary reporting treated Polymarket's token/airdrop as a future event after U.S. relaunch, distinct from pUSD collateral already used in trading infrastructure. Weight is limited because this is secondary reporting, not official Polymarket documentation.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T11:58:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"2b6994532a435d15d94f7ec3950ec92eaaf33931f20c6070810d53618b5c36b4\",\"size_bytes\":1747,\"source_description\":\"CoinDesk article page opened and extracted via web browser/search tool during defendant arguments. Secondary reporting; not an official Polymarket channel. Used to show market-context distinction between pUSD collateral and a future token/airdrop discussed by Polymarket CMO.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2025/10/24/polymarket-will-launch-token-and-airdrop-after-u-s-relaunch-cmo-says\",\"storage_name\":\"2b/2b6994532a435d15d94f7ec3950ec92eaaf33931f20c6070810d53618b5c36b4\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"CoinDesk secondary report: Polymarket future token and airdrop after U.S. relaunch\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T10:34:00Z\",\"evidence_id\":\